# Development Workflow

## Session Start Checklist

Every session:
- [ ] Read memory-bank/activeContext.md
- [ ] Read memory-bank/progress.md
- [ ] Check current task in _docs/task-list.md
- [ ] Ask about any blockers

## Memory Bank Management

For complete Memory Bank procedures, see @memory-bank-management.mdc

**Quick Reference:**
- Read activeContext.md and progress.md FIRST every session
- Update progress.md after completing tasks
- Update activeContext.md after significant changes
- Run "update memory bank" command for full review

**Integration with Workflow:**
Memory Bank updates are part of task completion (Step 4 - Report Completion).
Don't mark task complete without updating Memory Bank.

## Execution Modes

This project supports two execution modes:

- **Manual Mode** (default): Step-by-step with user approval at each stage
- **Autonomous Mode**: Continuous execution for batch tasks (see @autonomous-execution.mdc)

The workflows below apply to **Manual Mode**. For autonomous mode, see @autonomous-execution.mdc.

